Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最喜欢的发带借给剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.12,0:01:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是借给你而已一定要还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小姑娘看起来是你的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.07,0:02:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生气吧生气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.04,0:02:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就能回到十年前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恨我吧杀人者拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.62,0:02:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七话\N月下之生死决斗\N为保护所爱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么瞪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是捉你来吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.98,0:02:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙!正大光明的战斗\N赢不了剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把我捉来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.02,0:02:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在抽完一支烟前\N就能把他打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.79,0:03:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太无聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你当成人质的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋就会生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.27,0:03:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生气的家伙\N就能找回从前的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.64,0:03:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你。你。不知道剑心有多强吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.75,0:03:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幕府末年的杀人者拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有让人起鸡皮疙瘩般的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时侯我也在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新撰组的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新撰组？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫。你的剑沾上了你的血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们新撰组的耻辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分出胜败来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样在京都奋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的拔刀斋\N差一点就能杀他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.91,0:04:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣\N其他的事有这么有趣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.31,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心不一样\N跟只希望流血你不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心不会再成为杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿熏？被捉走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑笠指定决斗的场所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回不来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拜托署长先生把小熏救出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋打算一个人去救阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了分出杀人者和杀人者的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人者对杀人者。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剑心已经不是杀人者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他会输也说不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.53,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样那家伙\N也要一个人去战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等！等一下混帐东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我让我去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在以前发生什么事我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟幕府末年没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去帮助现在的剑心跟阿熏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在阻止你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了这东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了！章鱼不要太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才不要太慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要开始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.52,0:06:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那么有趣的人的时侯开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.66,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼神很好现在生气着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.77,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.67,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能阻止你\N让小熏小姐卷进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我。。？\N不对这不是平常的剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很好的杀气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下要把\N那奇怪的刀刃翻转过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样\N传说中的杀人王就复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.07,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这。。这是杀人王拔刀斋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.78,0:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发怒再发怒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你最厉害的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单手平突击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.22,0:07:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.05,0:07:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,横扫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始是十字型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破竹子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散掉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.82,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.98,0:08:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶到底在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.79,0:08:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点找到\N剑心和阿熏都会被作掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.56,0:08:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有呢\N跟以前的拔刀斋差太远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有想杀你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.44,0:08:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你倒地后抽三支烟的时候\N再把你杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太无聊了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点正气！你真是个魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再让你更生气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.65,0:09:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑。。。心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你。。对小熏小姐做了什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她心里打了一剂强针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.03,0:09:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让肺机能麻痹的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过不了五分钟就窒息死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破这种技术只有二种方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.01,0:10:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种是被施者\N靠自己的力量解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.55,0:10:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那必须拥有能超越我的剑气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人的话就非常不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.46,0:10:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的一种\N得施这种技术的我死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之不把我杀了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人就要死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.51,0:10:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？没时间了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想看这女人被杀死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？没时间了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想看这女人被杀死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因窒息而死\N那可是非常的难看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有讲话的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要说的话用那把剑来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那把不正常的刀。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.29,0:11:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现。现在的。不用说剑闪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连身体的动作也看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是飞天御剑流！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样杀人拔刀斋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩很好很好这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有讲话的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把你给杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点放马过来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.98,0:11:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑。剑。心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把我杀了吗\N太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常适合杀人者的台词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于回到原来的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个幕府末年！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人拔刀斋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行。。剑。。心不。。行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始才是真的胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了拔刀斋！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.58,0:12:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是传说中的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充满杀气后果然不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.89,0:12:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也。。从心里开始认真起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒最强的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心之一方是暗示对方\N让对方惊畏的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种技术如果反过来用的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是对自己本身的暗示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让自己所有\N潜在的能力发挥出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我！不败也！也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我！无敌！也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我！最强！也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心之一方的技影是“冯鬼之术“
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.34,0:13:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用这个是从新撰组出来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五年来的第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么技术\N只要你喜欢就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.26,0:13:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即然你说要杀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的死也最绝对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.55,0:13:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是！拔刀术的架势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在剑术剑套里猛然拔出\N使其加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间就把对手杀死的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这家伙的拔刀\N是非常的神速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同神一样的速度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放剑过来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋的名字的由来\N我会让你好好的品尝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是拔刀斋一击必有人死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开后是完全的无防备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀的瞬间如果改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是会改变吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.78,0:14:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让它改变吧！让它改变吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是逆刃刀的话\N在拔刀的一瞬间慢了一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会赢的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分出胜负吧！拔刀斋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.20,0:14:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了！拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑跟鞘的。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二段拔刀术。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.85,0:15:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流拔刀术“双龙闪”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逆刃刀是不适合拔刀术的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.73,0:15:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道的非常的清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.30,0:15:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀术的最极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是拔刀斋名字的由来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手关节被弄碎了筋也断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你使用剑的生命到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的人生也到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊。。剑。。。剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在犹豫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.80,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要解除那姑娘\N所中的”心之一方”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有把我给杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑。。。剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.51,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了救小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再一次的回到杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的杀人的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我刃卫领教看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑是凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑术是杀人术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么跟漂亮的事比\N那也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那事实比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.61,0:16:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如小熏小姐所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想法单纯来的喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.82,0:16:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑。。剑。。心。。剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.96,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要回到杀人者。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.81,0:17:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人剑。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏小姐振作！振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作。。。一点。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.77,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到”心之一方”\N也被这小姑娘给破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.78,0:17:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了刃卫单凭那只小刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.45,0:17:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何况只能用左手的家伙\N已经没有胜机了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.15,0:17:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部结束了乖乖的受绑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.63,0:18:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我来收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉真好。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要用那种眼神看我。。拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.62,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要杀我的时侯\N你的眼神更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.22,0:18:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的本性果然是杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.06,0:18:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样是杀人者所说的错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人者终究到死为止\N都要杀人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能成为其他人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.57,0:18:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你永远是流浪人吗。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.21,0:18:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在地狱的深处看着你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人者终究到死为止\N都要杀人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给警察吧。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了！脚印！是剑心的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真。真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.97,0:19:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的脚印连到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨。。笨蛋这是牛的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.98,0:19:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了我，笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊。阿熏！剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧我已经来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里呢！黑笠呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.90,0:19:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是无聊也不等我来救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因为整夜鼓劲在干\N现在肚子也饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.74,0:19:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨。。蛋也没做什么事\N为什么会肚子饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了吗小熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.65,0:20:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！谢谢你救了我。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先跟你道谢一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，小生才该跟你道谢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么。。？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.73,0:20:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候如果\N小熏小姐不阻止我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小生就完全返回到\N杀人的拔刀斋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不胜感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.70,0:20:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？什么不胜感激呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊不。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.34,0:20:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了该还你蓝色发带了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为伤口的血。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最中意的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.69,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了\N我们不是约定过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.73,0:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对。对不起小熏小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！不要踩我的脚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呢？约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟小孩子无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刃卫。。小生的本性是杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小生已不再杀人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.99,0:21:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到死为止都以流浪人而过活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这些同伴在
